# Agent System Rules

- The system prompt is assembled per-turn (architecture B) in `convertToLLMMessageService.ts`
- Tool definitions are in `prompts.ts` under `builtinTools`
- MCP tools are dynamically loaded and deduplicated (native builtins take priority)
- The `edit_file` sequential re-read rule is critical — never remove it from the prompt
- Model identity is injected from `modelSelection` to help the agent self-calibrate
- Workspace rules, skills, and rich context are appended to `aiInstructions` before being passed to `prepareMessages`
